body: HTML stands for Hyper Text Markup Language. It is a markup language used to create webpages. It creates the founding Structure of web-development.
CSS stands for Cascading Style Sheets. It is used to design and format the webpages.There are various ways in which CSS can be attatched to an HTML document.
